cdata.name: Content and AD Network
cdata.desc:
MobiPromo, a Singapore based Wireless company launched a blockchain-based content & advertisement delivery platform. The platform uses the ecosystem to link users Point-to-Point and create nodes around the globe. This way, when users and nodes are connected the advertises & content can be shared between all users in the ecosystem.

Built on Ethereum blockchain, the token CAN (ERC 20) serves as a payment method on MobiPromo's network and is required for advertisers to be able to use the advertising service.
